Package: groestlcoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Groestlcoin is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic cash system that
 is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or
 trusted parties.  Users hold the crypto keys to their own money and
 transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to
 check for double-spending.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, groestlcoind, and the CLI tool
 groestlcoin-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: groestlcoin-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Groestlcoin is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic cash system that
 is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or
 trusted parties.  Users hold the crypto keys to their own money and
 transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to
 check for double-spending.
 .
 This package provides Groestlcoin-Qt, a GUI for Groestlcoin based on Qt.

Package: groestlcoin-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Groestlcoin is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic cash system that
 is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or
 trusted parties.  Users hold the crypto keys to their own money and
 transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to
 check for double-spending.
 .
 This package provides groestlcoin-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a groestlcoin daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.

 Package: groestlcoin-wallet
 Architecture: any
 Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
 Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone wallet tool
  Groestlcoin is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic cash system that
  is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or
  trusted parties.  Users hold the crypto keys to their own money and
  transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to
  check for double-spending.
  .
  This package provides groestlcoin-wallet, a command-line offline tool for
  creating and interacting with Groestlcoin Core wallet file.
